      <h3>Teletype for Atom</h3>

      <p>Great things happen when developers work together—from teaching
      and sharing knowledge to building better software. Teletype for Atom
      makes collaborating on code just as easy as it is to code alone, right
      from your editor.</p>

      <div class="welcome-bgs">
        <img class="welcome-bg welcome-bg--screenshot" src="/assets/index-teletype-screenshot.png">
      </div>

